maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.text: Il est temps de combattre votre ennemi juré !

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.orig: Time to meet our pet again!
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.text: Il est temps de danser avec notre animal de compagnie !

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.orig: This time, we prepared a stage for you.
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.text: Cette fois, nous avons préparé toute une scène pour vous.
Il est temps de retrouver votre vieil ami !

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.orig: We took the liberty of modifying it a bit.
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.text: Nous avons pris la liberté de le modifier un peu.

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/285.orig: Now show us your best performance!

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.orig: We promised to measure the time. Behold!
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.text: Nous avions promis de mesurer le temps. Le voici !

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.orig: Why do you keep teasing us with this pose?
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.text: Pourquoi continuez-vous à nous narguer avec votre posture ?

maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.orig: Yes. This pose. We know it.
maps/autumn/extra-boss.json/entities/286.text: Oui. Cette posture. Nous la connaissons.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye just go into that big room to start the fight.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Va juste dans cette grande salle pour démarrer le combat.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: I'll keep track of the time ye take for it.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Je surveillerai le temps que tu mets pour réussir l'épreuve.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye just go into that big room to start the fight.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Va juste dans cette grande salle pour démarrer le combat.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: I'll keep track of the time ye take for it.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Je surveillerai le temps que tu mets pour réussir l'épreuve.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye back for another try or to see yer best time?
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: T'es de retour pour un nouvel essai ou pour voir ton meilleur temps ?

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye just go into the big room lass. I'll save the time for ye.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Va juste dans cette grande salle, fillette. Je m'occupe du temps.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: [nods]
Here ye go, lass.
Ye come back later then.
Try Challenge
View Highscore
Cancel
A good fight lass.
Ye wanna take a look at yer best times?
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Tu veux voir tes meilleurs temps ?

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: [nods]
Here ye go, lass.
[shakes head]
Alright. Ye come back later then. The challenge takes a while to be ready again.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: OK. Reviens plus tard alors. Le challenge met un petit moment avant d'être prêt à être réutilisé.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: [Yes]
[No]
Just like in the ol' days.
Still a big room inside a darn small building.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: C'est toujours une grande salle dans un satané petit bâtiment.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Them developers sure know how to make it look plausible.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Ces développeurs savent vraiment comment rendre ça plausible.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Well, the counter is still there. So I guess ye can take on the challenge.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Bon, le compteur est toujours là. Donc je pense que tu peux démarrer le combat.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye want to try it out?
[nods]
But ye better make sure ye're up to the task.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Mais sois sûr d'être bien préparée pour ça.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: The challenge here is pretty darn tough.
Heh, can't stop the lass from a fight.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Héhé, on ne peut pas empêcher la fillette de se battre.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Ye just go into that big room to start the battle.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Va juste dans cette grande salle pour démarrer le combat.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: I'll save the time ye need for it.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Je vais m'occuper du temps que tu mets.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: Now have some fun lass.
Survive!
Ye did it! Very good performance, lass.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: T'as réussie ! Très bonne performance, fillette.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: As promised I saved your time. So just talk to me to get an overview.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Comme promis, j'ai compté le temps. Donc viens me demander, si tu veux jeter un coup d'œil.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: However the challenge will need some time to be ready again.
maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.text: Mais le challenge va mettre un petit moment avant d'être prêt à nouveau.

maps/autumn/observatory-inner.json/entit.orig: And there's yer reward.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/16/s.orig: Time for turrets!\. Don't worry, those things won't hurt you.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/16/s.text: Maintenant, au tourelles !\. Oh t'inquiète pas, ces choses ne te feront pas mal.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/16/s.orig: This is in fact just a simple puzzle.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/16/s.text: En fait c'est juste un simple puzzle.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: C'mon, you can do this yourself.\. Really want a hint?
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Allez, tu peux faire ça par toi-même.\. Tu as vraiment besoin d'aide ?

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Oh well.\. Look, these blocks are kinda like switches.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Bon d'accord.\. Regarde, ces blocs sont un peu comme des interrupteurs.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Only they don't react to the typical balls.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: C'est juste qu'ils ne réagissent pas à des boules normales.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Maybe they react when hit by something else.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Peut-être qu'ils réagissent quand ils sont touchés par autre chose.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Attagirl! Use that pretty head of yours.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Ouais ! Utilise ta jolie petite tête.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Hm, this one is a tiny bit more tricky. Need some help?
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Hum, celui-là est un poil plus compliqué. Besoin d'aide ?

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: To make the turret hit these blocks you have to stand between turret and block.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Pour que la tourelle touche ces blocs, tu dois te trouver entre la tourelle et le bloc.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Then you need to dodge the bullet right after it was shot.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Ensuite il faut que tu évites le projectile juste après qu'il soit tiré.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: You need to get the timing right.\. C'mon, I know you can do it!
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Il faut avoir le bon timing.\. Allez, je sais que tu peux le faire !

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: It's actually almost the same as before.\. Only this time the turret and blocks are on a higher level.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: C'est presque la même chose qu'avant.\. Juste que cette fois la tourelle et le bloc sont à un étage supérieur.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: So get up on that container in the middle and dodge some bullets!
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Donc monte sur le conteneur au milieu et évite quelques projectiles !

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: These things are kinda unexpected, right?\. Need a hint?
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Ces choses sont un peu inattendues, non ?\. Besoin d'un indice ?

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: That mirror-like thing only shoots bullets, when it's hit by your balls.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Cette espèce de miroir ne tire des projectiles que quand il est touché par tes boules.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: And it always shoots the bullets right at you.
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Et il tire toujours ces projectiles vers toi.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: You'll need a block between you and the mirror and still need to hit the mirror with one of your balls...
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Il te faut un bloc entre toi et le miroir et que tu réussisses à lui tirer dessus avec tes boules.

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: So here's the hint:\. Think bouncing balls!
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Donc voilà l'indice :\. Pense à des boules rebondissantes !

maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.orig: Phew, that's all for this room.\. Lot's of puzzles, right?\. But don't worry, you will get some real action in the next room!
maps/cargo-ship/room3.json/entities/27/s.text: Pfiou, c'est tout pour cette salle.\. Ça faisait beaucoup de puzzles, non ?\. Mais ne t'inquiète pas, il va y avoir de l'action dans la prochaine salle !

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/4/set.text:
REGARDE UN PEU MES ICÔNES
NAN !
ça farte ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/4/set.orig: Please stop following me around, \s[6]you're creeping me out...
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/4/set.text: Arrête de me suivre partout, \s[6]tu me fais peur...

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/4/set.orig: I'm just here to do some serious talking. We have to check some layout bug here.
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/4/set.text: Je suis juste là pour faire des conversations sérieuses. Il faut que l'on vérifie un bug de mise en page là.

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: What's up, dawg?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Yo les mecs, ça boume ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: You're a quite one, aren't you?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Toujours silencieux, à ce que je vois ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Follow Carla!
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Suivez Carla !

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: What's up, dawg?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Yo les mecs, ça boume ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: You're a quite one, aren't you?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Toujours silencieux, à ce que je vois ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Follow Carla!
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Suivez Carla !

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Okay, so now you're leaving on me, huh?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Et maintenant tu me quittes ? Super.

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Don't you also feel a bit lonely around here?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Tu te sens pas un peu seul ici ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: I mean, it's not exactly the most crowded place, right?
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Je veux dire, ce n'est pas l'endroit le plus fréquenté, non ?

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Well, except for those robots. But those aren't nice, I tell you!
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Bon, peut être excepté ces robots. Mais ils ne sont pas gentils, crois-moi !

maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.orig: Trust me, I know from experience...
maps/cargo-ship/test.json/entities/6/set.text: Fais-moi confiance, je parle d'expérience...
